spec: abc_extra128
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(abc)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/abc.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/abc.html — Python abc module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/abc.py"
    - "CPython source: Modules/_abc.c"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: wave 256 theme — abc.ABCMeta method qualnames and abc.ABC.__init_subclass__ identity. NEW in extra128: abc.ABCMeta.__instancecheck__.__qualname__=='ABCMeta.__instancecheck__' (len=25); abc.ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__.__qualname__=='ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__' (len=25); abc.ABCMeta.register.__qualname__=='ABCMeta.register' (len=16); abc.ABCMeta._dump_registry.__qualname__=='ABCMeta._dump_registry' (len=22); abc.ABC.__init_subclass__.__qualname__=='ABC.__init_subclass__' (len=21); abc.ABCMeta.register.__code__.co_argcount==2; abc.ABCMeta.__instancecheck__.__code__.co_argcount==2; abc.ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__.__code__.co_argcount==2; abc.ABCMeta._dump_registry.__code__.co_argcount==2; abc.ABCMeta.__mro__.__len__()==3 (MRO=[ABCMeta, type, object]); abc.abstractmethod.__qualname__=='abstractmethod' (len=14). All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "abc.ABCMeta.__instancecheck__.__qualname__ == 'ABCMeta.__instancecheck__' (len=25). 'ABCMeta'=7 + '.'=1 + '__instancecheck__'=17 = 25. Same length as ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__ qualname. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "abc.ABC.__init_subclass__.__qualname__ == 'ABC.__init_subclass__' (len=21). ABC.__init_subclass__ is a builtin_function_or_method (not a Python function), so it has a __qualname__ but no __code__. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "abc.ABCMeta.__mro__.__len__() == 3. ABCMeta's MRO is [ABCMeta, type, object] — ABCMeta is a metaclass that inherits from type. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

